query:
UPDATE pages 
SET `order` = CASE id
  WHEN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM pages WHERE moduleId = 90002 ORDER BY `order`, id LIMIT 1) AS t1) THEN 1
  WHEN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM pages WHERE moduleId = 90002 ORDER BY `order`, id LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1) AS t2) THEN 2
  WHEN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM pages WHERE moduleId = 90002 ORDER BY `order`, id LIMIT 1 OFFSET 2) AS t3) THEN 3
  WHEN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM pages WHERE moduleId = 90002 ORDER BY `order`, id LIMIT 1 OFFSET 3) AS t4) THEN 4
  WHEN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM pages WHERE moduleId = 90002 ORDER BY `order`, id LIMIT 1 OFFSET 4) AS t5) THEN 5
  WHEN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT id FROM pages WHERE moduleId = 90002 ORDER BY `order`, id LIMIT 1 OFFSET 5) AS t6) THEN 6
END
WHERE moduleId = 90002;
